{"word":"G5377 - φιλόθεος - philótheos - fil-oth'-eh-os - Lover of God","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φιλόθεος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">philótheos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fil-oth'-eh-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Lover of God</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தேவப்பிரியரான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"loving, lovers of God"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5384 - φίλος - phílos - fee'-los/5384\">G5384</a> and <a href=\"#/G2316 - θεός - theós - theh'-os/2316\">G2316</a>; <i>fond of God</i>, that is, <i>pious:</i> - lover of God.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2705/2705\">G2705</a>, <a href=\"#/G5367/5367\">G5367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5368/5368\">G5368</a>, <a href=\"#/G5369/5369\">G5369</a>, <a href=\"#/G5370/5370\">G5370</a>, <a href=\"#/G5373/5373\">G5373</a>, <a href=\"#/G5377/5377\">G5377</a>, <a href=\"#/G5383/5383\">G5383</a>, <a href=\"#/G5384/5384\">G5384</a>, <a href=\"#/G5387/5387\">G5387</a>"}]}